 and upstream STAR records, and some greenfield/player-coach range is not yet promoted into the top reusable evidence layer for this category.","Representation quality lags evidence: the current headline is generic, the summary is dominated by one AdTech modernization story, and AI platform, evaluation, guardrails, and player-coach signals sit mostly in projects rather than the top profile narrative.","AI architecture fit is very strong because the record shows production platform architecture, event-driven systems, retrieval quality work, evaluation harnesses, structured outputs, guardrails, and live-system observability.","Leadership scope fit is good for a technical lead / architect / player-coach reading, but weaker for any executive-first interpretation because the evidence is stronger on technical direction, mentoring, and hiring participation than on org ownership.","Impact proof is strong because the record includes quantified outcomes across reliability, platform scale, onboarding, velocity, misalignment reduction, and AI platform usage."],"citations":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:28","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:71","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:88","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:163","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:182","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:217","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:250","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:9","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:27","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:44","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:94","data/master-cv/role_metadata.json:3","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:7","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:268","blueprint.category_signature","blueprint.core_competency_themes","blueprint.role_weighting_guidance"]},"strongest_supported_signals":[{"signal":"Production AI platform architecture with retrieval quality, evaluation, and guardrail-adjacent controls","why_it_matters_for_category":"This category rewards proof of production AI platform design and productization more than abstract AI-leadership language.","status":"supported_and_curated","evidence_refs":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:332","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:354","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9"],"citation":"Supported by curated Commander-4/Joyia role and project evidence showing a 2,000-user, 42-plugin enterprise AI platform with hybrid retrieval, LLM-as-judge reranking, evaluation harnesses, structured outputs, MCP tools, and per-silo guardrail injection; this aligns directly to the category’s platform-architecture and AI-productization emphasis."},{"signal":"Platform modernization plus measurable reliability and observability outcomes in live systems","why_it_matters_for_category":"The target market values architecture, delivery, scale, and reliability as the core proof set for senior AI-platform roles.","status":"supported_and_curated","evidence_refs":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:28","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:71","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:163","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:146"],"citation":"Supported by curated Seven.One evidence showing event-driven modernization on AWS, 75% incident reduction, 3 years zero downtime, a billions-of-events observability pipeline, MTTR reduction, and multi-million-user scaling work."},{"signal":"Business-to-technical translation and stakeholder alignment around platform decisions","why_it_matters_for_category":"This category explicitly rewards candidates who turn ambiguous business needs into technical execution and roadmap delivery.","status":"supported_and_curated","evidence_refs":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:250","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:266","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:44"],"citation":"Supported by curated evidence on technical-debt ROI stakeholder education, business-metric realization, risk communication under ambiguity, and stakeholder-led event storming/domain discovery."},{"signal":"Player-coach leadership through standards, mentoring, and practice shaping","why_it_matters_for_category":"The category prefers technical leadership and practice shaping over inflated org-builder claims.","status":"supported_and_curated","evidence_refs":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:88","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:182","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:60","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:94"],"citation":"Supported by curated evidence on DDD standards, onboarding and velocity improvement, mentoring 10+ senior engineers, promotions to lead roles, and leading a cross-functional SCRUM team with improved delivery predictability."},{"signal":"Hands-on implementation credibility in Python/TypeScript across AI and platform systems","why_it_matters_for_category":"The market is still senior-IC/player-coach heavy, so implementation credibility strengthens architectural claims.","status":"supported_and_curated","evidence_refs":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/projects/commander4_skills.json:2","data/master-cv/roles/03_ki_labs.md:27","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7"],"citation":"Supported by curated evidence showing direct TypeScript/Python implementation in AI platform search, gateway, and ba